_description: Track Builder Export - use this data to create VehicleModel for SBW

pivot._note: Set X to your track's horizontal position (e.g. 25.5 for left, -25.5 for right)

instructions: 1. Create model with bones: trackMovL0-105, trackRotL0-105 (same for R)
3. Override getBoneRotX, getBoneMoveY, getBoneMoveZ with generated code
4. Set trackAnimationLength in vehicle data JSON to 212
5. Each track bone offset = index * 2 (e.g. track5 uses t = leftTrack + 10)
